{"tid":1471542,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"機場賽後檢討","createTime":"2019-08-14T09:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T10:04:37.000Z","uid":263795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7294c516a33f550bc2f805f2290a5828bd875557","tid":1471542,"uid":263795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:50:46.000Z","msg":"琴日機場件事大家點睇？<br />\n我同幾個朋友傾過下啦，大家都覺得有d過火，令人有把柄。機場唔可以好似馬路咁玩，唔係擺住人地唔出外就得，冇得兜路行喎。第二，要㩒住個大陸記者係啱，但洗唔洗打到咁，用索帶索住呢？又或者索係啱，但係之後仲打，仲想除褲，係想點？第三，因為怕有鬼，同埋不割𥱊，我個人認為勇武開始唔聽人講，一俾d唔同意見就鬧人左膠，鬧人鬼。我希望勇武可以學識聆聽，如果唔係贏咗都失民心呀⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n大家又點睇？"},{"pid":"7b8c2dc9bb298a38267845e2f9ebf3b23faa0cd5","tid":1471542,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"完全諗唔明有乜問題，更唔明有乜做錯喎？<br />\n<br />\n你班和理非話要搞機場民生設施, 就預咗有市民不滿, 出現市民鬧返你轉頭既場面啦<br />\n2014年佔馬路民生設施, 原理都係一樣<br />\n你班和理非唔係一早預咗出現「群眾鬥群眾」場面咩？<br />\n<br />\n因為你係搞民生設施, 唔係搞政府機關呀<br />\n林鄭月娥政權仍然係舒舒服服咁暢順運作, HAPPY地睇你「群眾鬥群眾」, 拖得耐就失民心呀！<br />\n<br />\n只要政府機關一日暢順運作, 無論和理非或勇武, 都係會無作用架！<br />\n講咗N次, 明未呀你老母！<br />\n<br />\n勇武係機場又唔係衝禁區, 只係活捉福田公安同支那最大五毛《環球時報》參與荃灣恐襲記者<br />\n保護緊市民, 我就唔知有乜要做錯啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">內地公安及警察合作帶備木棍在機場製造騷亂，被現場示威者抓住</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462882\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462882</a><br />\n<br />\n事源係有手足係T1大叫有警察<br />\n咁我就追過去問佢有冇委任證<br />\n當時仲有另一個人同徐公安立刻轉身走<br />\n咁就有巴打上前擋住佢<br />\n結果佢地2個即刻跑走<br />\n第一時間就有巴打追住徐錦煬<br />\n而有另一批巴打追住另外一個<br />\n最後追到佢 有巴打影咗佢張身份證<br />\n叫 林志威<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEqtyNn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEqtyNn.png&h=56bb3170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCXb93A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCXb93A.jpg&h=66aac2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ESgsJoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESgsJoT.jpg&h=60d448f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上google查完後 林志威都係福田分局輔警<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Jrwo1aR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrwo1aR.jpg&h=f05879fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場的徐錦煬徐錦煬是深圳福田公安<br />\n官方戶籍系統內廣東省只有一個徐錦煬<br />\n<br />\nFACK CHECKED:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/QQX30j1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQX30j1.jpg&h=fc940090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6OwMdRC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OwMdRC.jpg&h=56f7607a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Z9k9bRt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ9k9bRt.png&h=65ca8365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6BXjzbc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6BXjzbc.png&h=7002386b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Yto3gpF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYto3gpF.png&h=8f6501f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e41d500fd76e6acfa7e885a4f83bbfaacf7746e0","tid":1471542,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1468897/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1468897/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">付國豪有份參加荃灣恐怖襲擊</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/zGHcc0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzGHcc0J.jpg&h=5ae9711f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在機場用界刀傷示威者後被圍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/qTNPdyN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqTNPdyN.png&h=2b93a0da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75316ed8e645580d5832f0d080d970a066344f9e","tid":1471542,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:55:20.000Z","msg":"［極重要］投個票，癱瘓先 定 宣傳先？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1471527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1471527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"224129bb51d1e35ee21d4736c8b36819518b6fa8","tid":1471542,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"我覺得塞係冇問題其實，琴日同過現場幾個外國遊客傾過計，佢地係明白冇怪責，仲有講有笑，佢地話因為自己國家都會有示威行動，所以唔覺呢啲係乜野。比較嬲同不滿嘅係大陸旅客，西方國家旅客真係少見嬲。<br />\n<br />\n至於啲公安大陸spy，綁起就算，下次唔好私型，雖然係興過火屎，但我地唔可以好似黑警咁，絕不傷害戰俘，贏公關。可接受，但要改善。<br />\n<br />\n至於捉鬼，免了，只要定下一啲行動規矩，例如機場不可衝，咁啲鬼就會原型畢露。琴日有個手足比人打到pk，點知係捉錯。"}]}